  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bc7\u0bb0 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bb4\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Morning power outage affects e-learning activities - Public Utilities Commission",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Janaka Ratnayake, chairman of the Public Utilities Commission, said it would be difficult to conduct school education online if there was a power outage in the morning.",
        "The Ministry of Education has announced that urban schools will be closed this week and educational activities will continue online.",
        "He said this when asked about the measures taken to prevent power outages in the morning.",
        "He further said that the power supply will be cut off in two phases during the day and night from Monday the 27th to the 3rd of next month.",
        "However, in the event of a power outage in the morning, it is not possible to conduct school education activities online.",
        "This is because in the current situation facing the country, it is not possible to give the same priority to the two issues of power outage and school education activities.",
        "However, the power outage will start at 1 pm on the 27th and will continue till the 3rd.",
        "Accordingly, the Public Utilities Commission has given permission for power cuts of one to 40 minutes during the day and one hour and 20 minutes at night in zones A to L and B from 27th to 3rd.",
        "However, there will be a 2-hour power outage from 6 am to 8 am on all days except the upcoming 2nd and 3rd in the Sea Zone.",
        "At the same time, there will be a 3-hour power outage in the MNO and YZ zones from 5 am to 8 am on all days except the upcoming 2nd and 3rd."
      ],
